    <stitle>EC-16 CONTROLLER - TROUBLESHOOTING - TESTING TRACTION CONTROL MODULATOR</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl0403209" svcproctype="troubleshoot" graphiccount="1">
        <title>TESTING TRACTION CONTROL MODULATOR</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0403212">Figure 12</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0403212" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g0403212" filename="../figg04/G0403212.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 12. Testing Traction Control Modulator</caption>
        </figure>
        <table id="hl0403239">
            <title>Testing Traction Control Modulator</title>
            <tgroup cols="5">
                <colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.79in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" colwidth="0.80in"/>
                <colspec colname="3" colwidth="2.02in"/>
                <colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.42in"/>
                <colspec colname="5" colwidth="1.15in"/>
                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="5" spanname="s1t5"/>
                <thead>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES-IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">NO-OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>With ignition ON, inspect EC-16 for illuminated LEDs. Is TRC only ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403240.xml" xrefid="hl0403240">TESTING ENGINE CONTROL MODULE
                                    WIRE HARNESS</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Are TRC and MOD LEDs ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Turn ignition OFF and remove 18 pin connector from EC-16. Check resistance between
                                pins D2 and D3. Resistance should be 10 to 12 ohms. Remove 30 pin connector and check
                                continuity between ground (A1, 2, 3) and D2 and D3. No continuity permitted. Resistance
                                correct and no continuity to ground?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Check condition of 18 pin connector. Clean, reconnect, turn ignition ON and pass
                                magnet over EC-16 RESET. Repeat
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403208.xml" xrefid="hl0403208">INITIAL START-UP
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Disconnect 2 pin connector at modulator and check resistance of connector half
                                attached to antilock traction relay. Resistance should be 10 to 12 ohms. Then check
                                continuity between ground on 30 pin connector (A1, 2, 3) and both pins on the 2 pin
                                connector leading to the modulator. No continuity permitted. Resistance correct and no
                                continuity to ground?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Repair or replace wire harness (from 18 pin connector to 2 pin connector).</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Replace antilock traction relay (modulator).</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </svcproc>
